WEBVTT

00:06.499 --> 00:07.840
(Respect copyright)

00:14.112 --> 00:20.704
♪Memories hold you back
from fulfilling your dreams♪

00:24.288 --> 00:30.432
♪Only by moving forward
can you find reunion♪

00:32.640 --> 00:35.872
♪Endings only mark new routes♪

00:36.096 --> 00:42.112
♪It's all part of the scenery♪

00:42.432 --> 00:45.856
♪To the horizon's call♪

00:45.920 --> 00:52.480
♪Your journey hasn't started♪

00:53.536 --> 00:57.472
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

00:57.472 --> 01:03.552
♪Let time embrace you
and wash away the past♪

01:03.840 --> 01:07.712
♪Put every twist behind you♪

01:07.712 --> 01:12.576
♪Drift leisurely through time♪

01:12.960 --> 01:15.680
♪Make headway against the wind♪

01:15.680 --> 01:18.667
♪Let mountains bow to your pace♪

01:18.720 --> 01:24.128
♪Rush towards a life without regret♪

01:24.640 --> 01:28.579
♪Let your nature burst free♪

01:30.240 --> 01:34.490
=The First Jasmine=

01:35.280 --> 01:37.776
=Episode 19=

01:39.160 --> 01:40.479
Have you heard the news?

01:40.960 --> 01:41.559
Yes.

01:41.680 --> 01:43.888
I heard Prince Ding was investigating
the Yuan Fang case.

01:44.080 --> 01:45.880
When the trail pointed
to the Eastern Palace,

01:45.880 --> 01:47.119
Mo Jingli set himself on fire.

01:49.160 --> 01:50.039
What do you think?

01:52.039 --> 01:54.160
Eight years ago,
the Eastern Palace pressed you hard,

01:54.160 --> 01:55.640
attempting to get you killed.

01:56.199 --> 01:59.360
If not for your immense fortune,
there would be no peace today.

02:00.080 --> 02:01.080
You showed benevolence,

02:01.399 --> 02:03.720
leaving their child alive
and titling him as a prince.

02:03.720 --> 02:06.479
Yet Mo Jingli harbored an ill ambition.

02:07.000 --> 02:08.480
He failed to appreciate your grace,

02:08.480 --> 02:11.040
even plotted secretly
and committed such a rebellious act.

02:11.240 --> 02:13.599
Such a source of disaster
must be eradicated completely.

02:14.040 --> 02:15.360
Lest it'll endanger the nation.

02:18.800 --> 02:21.240
Both of your share similar opinions.

02:27.200 --> 02:28.080
What do you think?

02:29.960 --> 02:31.599
You shall be the one to decide.

02:35.719 --> 02:36.760
Then investigate.

02:38.119 --> 02:41.080
Marquis Muyang, order
the Imperial Court of Judicial Review

02:41.279 --> 02:43.640
to guard all city gates
and key roads between wards.

02:43.800 --> 02:45.599
Execute any suspicious person.

02:46.448 --> 02:49.080
Everything related to
Mo Jingli and Eastern Palace,

02:49.399 --> 02:52.240
be it a letter, document, or witness,

02:52.599 --> 02:53.640
shall be captured.

02:54.080 --> 02:56.879
The Left and Right Gate Guards
strictly guard all palace entrances.

02:57.279 --> 02:59.480
No entry or exit is allowed
without my order.

02:59.920 --> 03:00.719
Yes.

03:05.360 --> 03:08.480
Back then, I told her not to keep
anyone of the Eastern Palace alive,

03:09.040 --> 03:10.879
but she insisted on
showing her benevolence.

03:11.399 --> 03:13.040
Can benevolence conquer the nation?

03:13.640 --> 03:15.200
Benevolence can rule the nation.

03:15.559 --> 03:17.960
Marquis Muyang,
if you don't change your mindset,

03:17.960 --> 03:19.279
you will betray her one day.

03:22.760 --> 03:25.760
Perhaps the only one
who truly understands her thoughts

03:26.320 --> 03:27.599
in this world is me.

03:32.080 --> 03:34.800
Do you think that fire
in the Eastern Palace

03:35.080 --> 03:36.800
started on its own?

03:40.679 --> 03:41.640
The matter is done.

03:42.679 --> 03:44.439
Are all traces thoroughly erased?

03:45.080 --> 03:47.960
It's merely an accident.
Your Majesty, Rest assured.

03:48.559 --> 03:51.879
However, this case will be handled
by Imperial Court of Judicial Review.

03:53.159 --> 03:54.599
If you wish to eradicate them,

03:55.024 --> 03:57.680
the post of Chief Minister
of Imperial Court of Judicial Review...

03:57.960 --> 04:00.624
Naturally, you'll be
the one to take on this post.

04:04.144 --> 04:05.760
After eliminating the Eastern Palace,

04:05.760 --> 04:08.599
it's only a matter of time
for you to reign the nation.

04:11.240 --> 04:13.119
Even though she's now
the Empress Dowager,

04:13.839 --> 04:15.879
whether she approves
of my methods or not,

04:16.680 --> 04:19.960
only I can deliver the result she wants.

04:20.839 --> 04:23.472
Every step on the road to power
is tainted by blood.

04:41.744 --> 04:48.336
(Imperial Court of Judicial Review)

04:48.880 --> 04:50.000
Guards, heed my command!

04:51.440 --> 04:54.399
Everyone implicated in Mo Jingli
and the Eastern Palace

04:54.799 --> 04:56.000
shall be captured.

04:56.839 --> 04:58.960
Better to detain everyone
than to let any go.

04:59.359 --> 05:02.279
Execute anyone who resist.

05:02.560 --> 05:03.359
- Yes!
- Yes!

05:07.159 --> 05:07.719
Don't move!

05:07.719 --> 05:08.440
Be careful!

05:09.120 --> 05:10.039
What's going on?

05:10.039 --> 05:10.880
That serious?

05:12.039 --> 05:13.520
This way! Hurry!

05:20.719 --> 05:21.440
Go away.

05:21.599 --> 05:22.960
How dare you trespass in here?

05:23.159 --> 05:25.320
Let go of me!
Which office do you belong to?

05:25.799 --> 05:27.039
We act by the imperial decree.

05:27.039 --> 05:27.719
Move!

05:27.960 --> 05:28.520
Hurry!

05:32.919 --> 05:33.599
You go that way.

05:36.520 --> 05:37.080
Get up!

05:37.520 --> 05:38.120
What's wrong?

05:38.120 --> 05:38.719
Move!

05:39.399 --> 05:40.200
Let me go!

05:40.200 --> 05:40.720
Move!

05:40.720 --> 05:44.719
(Prince Li's Mansion)

05:44.719 --> 05:45.719
Listen carefully.

05:45.719 --> 05:48.880
From now on, this is under the rule
of Imperial Court of Judicial Review!

05:49.239 --> 05:49.760
Go!

05:49.919 --> 05:50.599
Yes!

05:53.719 --> 05:54.352
Spread out.

06:02.239 --> 06:04.880
Your Highness, many guards
from Imperial Court of Judicial Review

06:04.912 --> 06:06.599
surrounded the entire mansion.

06:19.120 --> 06:20.599
What right do you have to arrest me?

06:20.599 --> 06:21.120
Move!

06:21.120 --> 06:22.200
Let me go!

06:22.200 --> 06:22.719
Move!

06:23.440 --> 06:24.039
Don't touch me!

06:24.039 --> 06:24.560
- Move!
- I'm innocent!

06:24.680 --> 06:25.200
Move!

06:25.200 --> 06:25.760
Hurry!

06:26.576 --> 06:27.600
I'm innocent!

06:29.479 --> 06:31.479
Anyone caught whispering
will also be detained.

06:56.120 --> 06:57.479
Still thinking about Prince Li?

07:00.839 --> 07:03.200
The Prince Li's mansion
has been inspected inside and out.

07:04.080 --> 07:05.279
The fire spread fast.

07:06.560 --> 07:08.080
Multiple crucial points were ignited.

07:08.440 --> 07:10.039
There were many incendiary materials.

07:10.680 --> 07:13.640
It shouldn't be a whim
but a premeditated plan.

07:15.359 --> 07:16.399
He probably knew

07:16.599 --> 07:19.359
his schemes were about to be exposed,

07:20.080 --> 07:21.359
so he did it deliberately.

07:24.560 --> 07:25.960
The Eastern Palace got overturned.

07:26.640 --> 07:28.760
As the only descendant
of the late Crown Prince,

07:29.239 --> 07:30.680
he's destined to die.

07:31.760 --> 07:34.200
He even survived
such desperate circumstances.

07:34.599 --> 07:36.279
Now, the case remains unresolved.

07:36.560 --> 07:38.159
It is far from a hopeless dead end.

07:38.640 --> 07:40.279
How could he set himself on fire?

07:41.000 --> 07:42.120
That's just not him.

07:55.279 --> 07:58.159
Li, if something's on your mind,

07:59.120 --> 08:00.200
you can tell me.

08:05.440 --> 08:06.159
I'm alright.

08:08.120 --> 08:11.200
Do your legs hurt
from all the moving around lately?

08:12.760 --> 08:13.440
No.

08:14.640 --> 08:16.640
I had Qingyu prepare
salt packs for warm compress.

08:17.120 --> 08:18.719
Qingyu, are they ready?

08:19.399 --> 08:20.399
Yes, Your Highness.

08:21.120 --> 08:22.039
Bring them here.

08:34.680 --> 08:37.280
Your legs just healed.
You mustn't catch a cold.

08:39.040 --> 08:40.999
I added mugwort leaves
to the salt packs,

08:42.080 --> 08:43.239
perfect for warm compress.

08:45.119 --> 08:47.639
Don't think that just because you

08:47.639 --> 08:49.680
can stand and walk now,

08:49.999 --> 08:52.320
then you're fully healed
and have no restrictions.

08:53.719 --> 08:55.599
Even now, you shouldn't
stand for too long,

08:55.999 --> 08:58.800
run fast, or fight anyone.

09:01.119 --> 09:01.719
Yao.

09:03.479 --> 09:06.080
Consider it for me
and for Prince Ding's Mansion.

09:06.839 --> 09:09.519
Sister-in-law, Wuyou, and I,

09:09.999 --> 09:11.639
we all count on you.

09:17.519 --> 09:18.719
Does that feel better?

09:21.519 --> 09:22.479
Much better.

09:24.400 --> 09:25.519
You must be exhausted.

09:26.280 --> 09:27.719
Don't worry about me anymore.

09:28.280 --> 09:30.639
Get some rest today, okay?

09:36.816 --> 09:41.200
(Jingzhao Prefecture)

09:41.200 --> 09:41.879
Halt!

09:41.920 --> 09:44.280
Your Highness!

09:46.879 --> 09:49.119
You are finally back.
Something terrible has happened!

10:01.119 --> 10:01.879
What?

10:02.719 --> 10:06.119
Prince Ding, are you here
to get involved in it?

10:09.719 --> 10:10.879
Such poor timing.

10:11.320 --> 10:14.400
I act by the Empress Dowager's decree.

10:15.119 --> 10:16.320
Anyone connected to Mo Jingli

10:16.719 --> 10:18.879
or any guilty officials
from the Eastern Palace,

10:19.040 --> 10:20.680
shall receive a thorough investigation.

10:20.879 --> 10:22.599
I've told you many times.

10:22.879 --> 10:25.479
I have no connection
to the Eastern Palace!

10:25.479 --> 10:27.879
Shut it! How dare you deny?

10:29.080 --> 10:30.280
Your Fourth Uncle

10:30.639 --> 10:32.879
was a worker bought
by the Eastern Palace back then.

10:33.400 --> 10:36.879
Coming and going daily,
who knows who he interacted with

10:36.920 --> 10:38.719
or what business he handled for them.

10:39.200 --> 10:40.040
And you

10:40.960 --> 10:44.800
just happened to be present
at the ambush scene in Penglai Alley.

10:45.280 --> 10:47.920
Now that Mo Jingli committed suicide
out of fear of punishment,

10:47.920 --> 10:49.080
so the lead is cut.

10:49.519 --> 10:51.280
I have every reason to suspect you

10:51.400 --> 10:53.280
to be deeply involved in this case.

10:53.400 --> 10:55.239
As the Military Secretary,

10:55.680 --> 10:57.639
I went to Penglai Alley on duty!

11:01.280 --> 11:03.280
What a Military Secretary!

11:04.040 --> 11:04.920
Don't fret.

11:05.712 --> 11:07.408
At the Imperial Court
of Judicial Review,

11:07.800 --> 11:10.280
I will hear your excuses carefully.

11:14.519 --> 11:17.280
Prince Ding, any objection

11:18.119 --> 11:19.280
to my words?

11:20.519 --> 11:23.280
Or, any objection

11:24.119 --> 11:25.200
to Her Majesty's decree?

11:37.040 --> 11:38.800
Her Majesty sent you
to investigate the case,

11:39.759 --> 11:43.400
not to randomly slander
and frame decent men.

11:44.479 --> 11:45.280
Decent men?

11:48.719 --> 11:51.479
Whether he's a decent man,
it's not up to you.

11:52.359 --> 11:53.839
We'll know after my investigation.

11:55.519 --> 11:56.599
Mo Jingli

11:57.040 --> 11:59.200
seemed so decent before.

11:59.879 --> 12:01.719
He was so respectful
to the Empress Dowager

12:02.239 --> 12:03.680
and the Emperor,

12:04.200 --> 12:05.680
not a single fault found.

12:06.400 --> 12:07.680
Now his schemes are exposed,

12:08.119 --> 12:12.080
only then did I realize
that he had long harmed ill intentions,

12:12.479 --> 12:14.639
playing the fool all along.

12:15.680 --> 12:16.879
Her Majesty is benevolent.

12:19.960 --> 12:21.320
But I know well

12:23.200 --> 12:26.879
that to eliminate evil thoroughly,
we must eradicate it at its root.

12:28.080 --> 12:33.080
Some things left alive
will eventually become disasters.

12:37.759 --> 12:39.280
After I finish my investigation,

12:40.160 --> 12:42.080
I'll give you an explanation.

12:44.040 --> 12:44.639
Take him away.

12:45.440 --> 12:45.960
Yes!

12:51.440 --> 12:52.280
Deputy Prefect Zheng,

12:54.920 --> 12:56.280
come with me.

13:01.080 --> 13:01.719
Yes!

13:09.040 --> 13:09.719
Shut the door.

13:37.920 --> 13:39.479
You...

13:41.280 --> 13:42.119
What?

13:44.280 --> 13:46.040
Do you really think I fear you?

13:47.080 --> 13:48.839
Have you forgotten that?

13:49.479 --> 13:51.879
I once fought in fierce battlefields

13:52.999 --> 13:56.519
and killed more men than you knew.

13:57.519 --> 14:01.119
You fear Marquis Muyang, but not me?

14:01.879 --> 14:03.280
You're using illegal punishment.

14:03.839 --> 14:05.879
How dare you treat me this way?

14:06.400 --> 14:08.879
I'll impeach you to the Empress Dowager.

14:09.280 --> 14:10.400
Talk law with me?

14:10.400 --> 14:11.239
Give me the law book.

14:19.879 --> 14:21.639
Open your eyes and read it carefully.

14:22.040 --> 14:24.800
Any one of these laws could convict you.

14:27.400 --> 14:29.800
You useless parasite!

14:36.119 --> 14:37.999
Abusing the power
of Jingzhao Prefecture,

14:37.999 --> 14:39.999
you've done many dirty schemes
all these years.

14:40.400 --> 14:42.040
Think you can hide them?

14:43.080 --> 14:43.999
Believe me or not,

14:44.839 --> 14:46.879
even if I kill you today,

14:47.519 --> 14:49.599
no one would dare speak for you.

14:53.119 --> 14:55.080
Were you present
during Qiu Xian's interrogation?

14:56.040 --> 14:58.119
You told Marquis Muyang
about everything?

15:00.879 --> 15:03.400
I know your every move.

15:03.800 --> 15:05.119
I spared you

15:05.639 --> 15:07.719
just to see what you're up to.

15:10.280 --> 15:11.599
But now,

15:13.400 --> 15:14.400
you're useless.

15:15.519 --> 15:16.280
Your Highness.

15:20.239 --> 15:20.920
Your Highness.

15:21.440 --> 15:25.040
As colleagues, we share life and death.

15:26.040 --> 15:27.320
If Wang Suwu dies,

15:28.719 --> 15:29.879
you won't live either.

15:30.400 --> 15:31.719
Your Highness!

15:31.719 --> 15:33.280
Your Highness, spare me!

15:33.440 --> 15:34.519
I won't do it again.

15:34.719 --> 15:35.599
Take him away!

15:35.639 --> 15:37.280
Your Highness, spare me!

15:37.400 --> 15:39.280
No! Your Highness, I won't do it again.

15:39.280 --> 15:40.999
Your Highness!

15:41.008 --> 15:42.128
(Jingzhao Prefecture)

15:47.800 --> 15:48.400
Your Highness.

15:49.920 --> 15:53.080
Marquis Muyang captured Wang Suwu
to make an example of him.

15:53.680 --> 15:55.160
We can't just sit back.

15:55.719 --> 15:57.519
We need to rescue Wang Suwu.

15:58.680 --> 15:59.879
And we need to get rid

16:00.200 --> 16:02.119
of Zheng Zuoshi,

16:02.320 --> 16:03.519
that traitor.

16:03.599 --> 16:04.464
Rest assured.

16:04.464 --> 16:07.024
We have planted agents in
the Imperial Court of Judicial Review.

16:07.024 --> 16:08.040
I've already sent word,

16:08.040 --> 16:10.239
ordering them
to keep an eye on Wang Suwu.

16:10.239 --> 16:12.119
Report any trouble immediately.

16:13.960 --> 16:14.759
One more thing.

16:15.280 --> 16:17.264
You go investigate
the Prince Li's Mansion again,

16:17.719 --> 16:19.800
including nearby places like Jvde Tower,

16:20.080 --> 16:23.440
Dehua Ward, Banruo Temple,
Taiping Ward, and other areas.

16:24.080 --> 16:27.119
Check if there's any hidden passage
or canal connecting to the mansion.

16:27.239 --> 16:30.280
But we already found
Prince Li's remains in the ruins, right?

16:32.519 --> 16:35.040
The remains' features
were too damaged to recognize.

16:36.040 --> 16:37.040
Not solid proof.

16:38.519 --> 16:39.440
We must find him,

16:40.080 --> 16:42.719
alive or dead.

16:42.719 --> 16:45.040
The Prince Li case is now handled
by Imperial Court of Judicial Review.

16:45.040 --> 16:46.719
It's hard for us to interfere.

16:48.519 --> 16:49.280
Your Highness.

16:51.200 --> 16:53.239
Your Highness, urgent news
from Prince Li's Mansion.

16:53.879 --> 16:55.200
Princess Li committed suicide.

17:15.519 --> 17:18.279
Princess Li was already heartbroken
over Prince Li's death.

17:18.600 --> 17:20.279
Out of grief, she tried to kill herself.

17:20.960 --> 17:23.279
Fortunately, a servant
found her and saved her.

17:23.999 --> 17:26.640
Marquis Muyang, you want
to take her for interrogation now.

17:27.039 --> 17:28.559
Do you aim to kill her?

17:31.519 --> 17:33.120
How is Princess Li?

17:35.440 --> 17:36.640
Marquis Muyang,

17:37.120 --> 17:38.640
luckily, she was found in time.

17:39.079 --> 17:40.640
Her life is not in immediate danger.

17:41.440 --> 17:43.680
She only needs proper rest.

17:48.559 --> 17:49.440
Her Majesty's decree

17:49.759 --> 17:51.920
only said to seal the mansion
and arrest remnants.

17:52.120 --> 17:54.360
Did it mention imprisoning Princess Li?

17:56.559 --> 17:57.712
Prince Li plotted treason.

17:58.400 --> 18:00.640
How can his family escape implication?

18:01.680 --> 18:03.079
I don't escape implication.

18:03.759 --> 18:05.360
I want to join him in death.

18:08.120 --> 18:11.440
Marquis Muyang, I know
you're ordered to investigate officials

18:11.600 --> 18:12.880
to investigate the case.

18:12.880 --> 18:14.239
But so far,

18:14.600 --> 18:16.239
I think you haven't secured

18:16.519 --> 18:18.120
one confession or a letter as evidence.

18:18.719 --> 18:22.079
What now? You want to drive
a princess consort to her death?

18:22.680 --> 18:25.840
It's the Empress Dowager herself
who bestowed this marriage.

18:27.400 --> 18:29.880
Your Highness, what do you mean?

18:30.519 --> 18:32.799
You cannot take her.

18:34.319 --> 18:37.519
If I leave her and trouble occurs...

18:37.519 --> 18:38.479
If trouble occurs,

18:39.519 --> 18:42.680
I will personally enter the palace
and apologize to the Empress Dowager.

18:46.600 --> 18:47.216
Fine.

18:48.600 --> 18:49.296
Let's go.

19:08.880 --> 19:11.920
Did you see his remains yesterday?

19:25.960 --> 19:27.840
The night when the edict
of marriage was issued,

19:28.799 --> 19:30.279
I was too happy to sleep.

19:31.079 --> 19:32.840
I ran into the courtyard
to count the stars

19:33.559 --> 19:34.719
and told myself,

19:36.360 --> 19:38.079
the number of stars I counted

19:39.279 --> 19:41.360
would be the number of years
I'd be with Prince Li.

19:44.519 --> 19:46.079
I counted over a hundred.

19:47.519 --> 19:49.440
I was so happy
that I could grow old with him.

19:51.600 --> 19:53.479
But we married only half a year ago.

19:54.519 --> 19:56.400
Only about a hundred days.

19:59.920 --> 20:01.319
So every single star

20:01.759 --> 20:03.920
could only count for one day.

20:07.279 --> 20:08.079
If I'd known it,

20:10.079 --> 20:11.479
I would've counted until dawn.

20:13.880 --> 20:14.960
You once asked me.

20:16.440 --> 20:18.600
Before my marriage,
I hadn't met Your Highness much.

20:18.928 --> 20:20.279
What do I like about him?

20:22.719 --> 20:26.279
But love doesn't have to bloom
from meeting someone in person, right?

20:27.920 --> 20:29.440
I read his poems.

20:30.840 --> 20:32.039
I heard the music he composed.

20:34.360 --> 20:36.600
Within his words and music,

20:37.400 --> 20:38.559
I already came to know him.

20:40.559 --> 20:42.759
And I know so much about him.

20:45.680 --> 20:47.279
Because of all these small things,

20:49.120 --> 20:50.719
he came to occupy a place in my heart.

20:51.519 --> 20:52.519
Isn't that okay?

20:54.479 --> 20:56.719
Can't one just love someone one-sided?

20:58.120 --> 21:00.519
Is one-sided love deemed worthless?

21:01.680 --> 21:03.680
I'd do anything for him.

21:06.079 --> 21:07.239
I truly

21:08.440 --> 21:10.799
used all my strength to love him.

21:13.120 --> 21:14.799
Actually, I should have hated you.

21:16.999 --> 21:18.279
You're arrogant and domineering.

21:18.999 --> 21:21.239
Your mother is greedy and shortsighted.

21:22.200 --> 21:24.319
Though what happened to me
doesn't relate to you two,

21:25.160 --> 21:26.880
I should have hated you.

21:27.719 --> 21:28.479
Do you understand?

21:34.120 --> 21:35.079
But I don't hate you.

21:36.319 --> 21:38.319
Because you're so naive.

21:39.279 --> 21:41.279
I can't resent a fool.

21:43.440 --> 21:44.920
But even a fool like you,

21:46.079 --> 21:47.840
is too good for that Mo Jingli.

21:50.719 --> 21:52.440
Loving someone is a wonderful thing.

21:53.400 --> 21:56.319
But you can't just devote yourself in it
without knowing anything.

21:57.279 --> 21:59.479
Mo Jingli is the son
of the late Crown Prince.

21:59.960 --> 22:01.600
He's the descendant
of the Eastern Palace.

22:01.880 --> 22:03.759
That means, he might

22:03.759 --> 22:05.840
set a raging fire at any moment,

22:06.519 --> 22:08.799
burning himself
and everything around him to ashes.

22:10.880 --> 22:13.440
Ye Ying, you said you love him.

22:14.600 --> 22:18.096
But when he set that fire,
did he think of you?

22:23.160 --> 22:26.319
When we were young,
we both studied the Zhuangzi.

22:27.440 --> 22:28.600
There was a saying in it,

22:29.519 --> 22:31.999
"Those with deep cravings
have shallow understanding."

22:33.279 --> 22:34.032
Remember it?

22:41.120 --> 22:42.600
I need to ask you one thing.

22:46.239 --> 22:47.039
Go ahead.

22:48.759 --> 22:51.319
That night,
when His Highness sent me away,

22:51.999 --> 22:53.640
he said something strange to me.

22:54.400 --> 22:55.200
What did he say?

22:56.279 --> 22:57.072
He said,

23:01.840 --> 23:03.279
"I'm sorry I failed you."

23:04.600 --> 23:06.200
"So be obedient and go."

23:07.920 --> 23:09.200
"If fate permits,"

23:09.999 --> 23:12.039
"we may meet again someday."

23:14.160 --> 23:17.200
Ye Li, you're smart.

23:18.279 --> 23:19.319
Figure this out for me.

23:20.519 --> 23:23.824
Does what he said indicate
that he might still be alive?

23:39.999 --> 23:41.120
Mo Xiuyao said

23:41.759 --> 23:44.440
he and Marquis Muyang reached
Prince Li's mansion at the same time.

23:45.039 --> 23:47.079
(Prince Li's Mansion)
Then guards sealed off the mansion.

23:47.960 --> 23:49.759
The fire spread fast.

23:50.120 --> 23:51.920
There were many incendiary materials.

23:52.880 --> 23:55.024
So Mo Jingli couldn't escape from fire.

23:58.759 --> 24:01.880
Li, how is Princess Li?

24:02.960 --> 24:03.559
She's fine now.

24:05.999 --> 24:08.279
I thought you two are at odds.

24:09.680 --> 24:10.880
Indeed.

24:11.759 --> 24:13.279
But she is still my sister.

24:13.759 --> 24:14.840
After all,

24:15.160 --> 24:17.840
neither she nor her mother
has ever done anything truly heinous.

24:21.479 --> 24:22.400
Then let's go back.

24:32.279 --> 24:32.976
Let's go.

24:33.920 --> 24:34.559
Okay.

24:40.528 --> 24:42.519
(Marquis Muyang's Mansion)

24:42.519 --> 24:44.799
Father!

24:46.440 --> 24:47.880
What are you doing?

24:49.200 --> 24:50.999
Take a look. Something wonderful.

24:52.079 --> 24:53.520
This thing's called

24:53.520 --> 24:54.192
- coconut.
- Coconut.

24:55.640 --> 24:56.759
Father, you know this?

24:57.160 --> 24:58.880
I used to drink this
frequently in Lingnan.

24:59.400 --> 25:00.640
Father, listen to me.

25:00.640 --> 25:02.999
This coconut isn't like
the ones from Lingnan.

25:03.360 --> 25:06.079
It came across the ocean
from South Seas.

25:06.239 --> 25:07.880
There are few even in the capital.

25:08.039 --> 25:08.880
Here, try it.

25:08.880 --> 25:10.360
No. It's too sweet for me.

25:10.400 --> 25:12.479
They say this relieves
summer heat, not sweet at all.

25:12.479 --> 25:13.680
Come on, try it.

25:13.680 --> 25:14.279
You drink it.

25:14.279 --> 25:16.440
Just try it. Try it.

25:16.440 --> 25:17.640
Fine, just a little.

25:17.640 --> 25:18.279
Okay.

25:23.479 --> 25:24.880
How is it? Delicious?

25:25.999 --> 25:26.960
Look at this top.

25:27.248 --> 25:29.520
Put it on the head.
Does it look like a black gauze cap?

25:59.120 --> 26:02.032
(Lakeview Garden)

26:30.079 --> 26:30.799
Marquis Muyang.

26:31.160 --> 26:31.960
Alright.

26:32.960 --> 26:35.479
I heard you've been
looking for manors recently.

26:35.600 --> 26:36.559
Found any?

26:39.360 --> 26:41.039
Haven't found the right one just yet.

26:41.799 --> 26:42.840
Then don't look for it.

26:43.640 --> 26:45.400
Plenty of empty rooms in here.

26:46.039 --> 26:47.039
Just pick one.

26:48.960 --> 26:50.400
This room is quite nice.

26:51.440 --> 26:54.440
You can live in this room.
Just settle down.

26:55.999 --> 26:57.600
So you can

26:57.840 --> 26:59.960
chat and talk with me.

27:01.440 --> 27:02.360
Thanks, Marquis Muyang.

27:03.039 --> 27:04.759
Here. Let me show you something good.

27:07.360 --> 27:08.120
This is

27:09.600 --> 27:10.319
called Coconut.

27:10.799 --> 27:12.279
Tianyang brought it back.

27:12.999 --> 27:14.279
I've tried it before.

27:14.840 --> 27:16.960
Too sweet for my taste.

27:17.479 --> 27:20.079
I thought you young folks might like it.

27:20.279 --> 27:21.440
So I brought it to you.

27:23.559 --> 27:25.079
I've already opened it for you.

27:26.759 --> 27:27.479
Try it.

27:29.559 --> 27:32.239
Young Lord gave this to you.

27:32.999 --> 27:34.160
I think it's improper.

27:34.640 --> 27:36.079
It's just food.

27:36.079 --> 27:37.079
Don't mind that much.

27:37.079 --> 27:38.160
Here, take it.

27:39.559 --> 27:40.144
Take it.

27:41.840 --> 27:42.600
Thank you.

27:42.999 --> 27:43.632
Try it.

27:45.440 --> 27:46.064
Come on.

27:50.759 --> 27:51.799
I almost forgot.

27:51.799 --> 27:54.039
Tianyang said to use this bamboo straw

27:54.239 --> 27:55.840
to suck out the juice inside.

27:55.960 --> 27:56.560
Take it.

27:57.680 --> 27:58.279
Try it.

27:59.759 --> 28:00.479
Go on.

28:01.239 --> 28:01.968
Yes.

28:09.079 --> 28:09.680
How's it?

28:11.559 --> 28:12.239
It's sweet.

28:12.999 --> 28:15.039
I knew you young folks would like it.

28:17.559 --> 28:21.440
Tianyang said this thing
looks like a black gauze cap.

28:21.680 --> 28:24.999
To me, it looks more like a flowerpot.

28:25.360 --> 28:26.960
Perfect for planting flowers.

28:28.920 --> 28:29.640
What do you think?

28:30.559 --> 28:31.360
Drink it.

28:34.920 --> 28:37.840
Look, it's all over you.

28:40.600 --> 28:41.120
Drink it.

28:41.799 --> 28:42.600
Yes.

28:48.240 --> 28:49.600
(Someone like Mo Jingli,)

28:49.759 --> 28:52.560
(vindictive, valuing life above all,)

28:53.039 --> 28:54.600
(before reaching his dead end,)

28:54.960 --> 28:56.360
(he wouldn't kill himself.)

28:57.552 --> 28:59.216
(He probably escaped using the fire.)

29:03.024 --> 29:03.880
(Record of Huai River Dredging)

29:03.880 --> 29:05.680
I've found all the things you wanted.

29:06.960 --> 29:09.799
I even dug out the items
at the bottom of the storage for you.

29:09.799 --> 29:11.759
Here's the Chronicle
of Yongzhou Prefecture.

29:12.208 --> 29:14.000
This is the Record
of Huai River Dredging.

29:14.200 --> 29:16.600
And this,
Capital Underground Waterways Map.

29:19.279 --> 29:20.160
And this one.

29:20.360 --> 29:23.160
I heard it's from
the reign of Emperor Taizu,

29:23.559 --> 29:24.816
(Dehua Ward Development Map)
the original survey map

29:24.816 --> 29:25.999
from the capital's reconstruction.

29:25.999 --> 29:27.279
This is a treasure.

29:28.440 --> 29:29.079
Look at you.

29:29.719 --> 29:31.999
You studied celestial phenomena
a while ago,

29:32.240 --> 29:33.968
and now underground waterways maps?

29:34.279 --> 29:35.799
What exactly are you up to?

29:38.160 --> 29:39.160
I have my reasons.

29:41.600 --> 29:44.160
Fine. I'll leave them to you.
I have work to do.

29:56.079 --> 29:59.279
The capital has a total of 108 wards.

29:59.360 --> 30:02.799
Wards and markets connect,
and streets crisscross.

30:03.279 --> 30:04.079
They excavated

30:05.319 --> 30:08.960
the Longshou, Qingming, and Yong'an

30:09.039 --> 30:11.759
canals as the backbone,
with branch canals forming a net,

30:11.840 --> 30:12.880
densely spread underneath

30:13.039 --> 30:16.120
(West Market, East Market, Dehua Ward)
West Market, East Market, Dehua Ward,

30:16.120 --> 30:18.039
(Renshou Ward, Chongren Ward)
Renshou Ward,

30:18.039 --> 30:19.479
(Xianzhu Ward)
and Chongren Ward.

30:20.640 --> 30:22.704
(Prince Li's Mansion
directly faces Dehua Ward.)

30:23.200 --> 30:25.960
(Mo Jingli only needs to dig
a secret passage from his mansion)

30:26.768 --> 30:28.624
(to the underground canal
beneath Dehua Ward,)

30:29.039 --> 30:30.512
(then leaves via that canal.)

30:30.759 --> 30:32.759
(To its west flows a small river.)

30:32.944 --> 30:35.824
(There must be an underground canal exit
nearby leading to the river.)

30:36.160 --> 30:37.719
(Perhaps he'll take that route.)

30:37.744 --> 30:39.152
(Dehua Ward)

30:40.999 --> 30:42.319
Dehua Ward.

31:45.479 --> 31:46.640
Why are you following me?

31:48.799 --> 31:50.200
You saved my life once before,

31:50.239 --> 31:51.640
then I almost got you killed.

31:51.999 --> 31:54.200
All in all, I owe you two lives.

31:54.400 --> 31:56.279
If I don't repay you, this unsettles me,

31:56.479 --> 31:57.640
and we can't be even.

31:58.799 --> 32:01.160
No need. Stop following me.

32:06.608 --> 32:09.648
Your Highness, the Imperial Court
of Judicial Review sent the person back.

32:25.920 --> 32:26.840
Your Highness.

32:27.039 --> 32:27.760
Don't move.

32:27.920 --> 32:28.784
Rest assured.

32:29.968 --> 32:32.440
I won't die that easily.

32:33.920 --> 32:34.920
Send him home.

32:35.319 --> 32:36.759
Find Physician Guan to treat him.

32:37.079 --> 32:37.880
- Yes!
- Yes!

32:45.759 --> 32:47.120
That traitor Zhou Jing!

32:50.279 --> 32:51.536
What about Prince Li's Mansion?

32:51.840 --> 32:53.120
Still impossible to investigate?

32:53.440 --> 32:55.360
It's quite tightly guarded.

32:55.360 --> 32:56.920
Our people got driven away

32:56.920 --> 32:59.472
by guards under the pretext
of protecting the scene.

33:04.144 --> 33:08.144
(Capital Underground Waterways Map)

33:13.840 --> 33:16.479
(That night,
when His Highness sent me away,)

33:17.120 --> 33:18.759
(he said something strange to me.)

33:19.640 --> 33:20.880
"If fate permits,"

33:21.680 --> 33:23.719
"we may meet again someday."

33:26.559 --> 33:29.559
Ye Li, you're smart.

33:30.680 --> 33:31.759
Figure this out for me.

33:32.920 --> 33:36.559
Does what he said indicate
that he might still be alive?

33:50.079 --> 33:52.559
Your Highness, a message from Prince Ding.

33:52.559 --> 33:54.379
He said due to
heavy official duties tonight,

33:54.379 --> 33:55.680
he won't return to the mansion.

33:56.559 --> 33:57.360
Understood.

33:58.200 --> 33:58.999
Yes.

34:21.519 --> 34:22.320
Come out.

34:27.679 --> 34:30.360
You've followed me this far,
aren't you going to lend a hand?

34:36.440 --> 34:38.559
Weren't you saying you owe me lives?

34:41.920 --> 34:43.920
You want me to kill all of them?

34:47.760 --> 34:48.559
Come with me.

34:57.720 --> 34:58.960
We enter from here.

34:59.280 --> 35:01.240
For height like this, no problem.

35:01.280 --> 35:03.119
I can enter without this.

35:04.159 --> 35:05.079
I need it.

35:05.360 --> 35:06.440
Neither do you.

36:00.320 --> 36:01.840
It's pitch-black in here.

36:01.920 --> 36:03.159
What are you looking for?

36:03.840 --> 36:04.639
Quiet!

36:26.320 --> 36:30.032
(The key to the hydraulic mechanism
lies in leveraging the power of water)

36:30.320 --> 36:31.728
(to maintain the balance.)

36:32.159 --> 36:33.360
Looking for a secret passage?

36:35.360 --> 36:36.559
That's my thing.

36:36.559 --> 36:39.280
For hidden mechanisms or passages,
the most crucial thing

36:40.320 --> 36:42.440
is to first find its...

36:43.519 --> 36:44.679
Go fetch a bucket of water.

36:45.760 --> 36:46.559
Water?

36:46.880 --> 36:48.280
Go, hurry.

37:06.440 --> 37:07.280
Pour it in

37:07.840 --> 37:09.479
slowly, at a steady pace.

37:57.519 --> 37:58.559
Where is this place?

37:59.240 --> 38:00.679
The capital's underground waterways.

38:00.880 --> 38:03.559
Based on the Water Control Records
from the Ministry of Works,

38:03.559 --> 38:05.360
these were built
during the previous dynasty,

38:06.119 --> 38:07.720
to drain the flooding in the capital,

38:08.479 --> 38:10.280
and to bring living water
into the palace.

38:11.280 --> 38:12.280
It cost quite a fortune

38:12.999 --> 38:14.240
and took decades to complete.

38:16.599 --> 38:17.400
This way.

38:24.519 --> 38:25.960
There are several passages here.

38:26.360 --> 38:27.360
Which one do we take?

38:28.440 --> 38:29.720
There must be place names here.

38:29.840 --> 38:30.760
Look for them.

38:39.240 --> 38:40.479
(Jvde Tower)
Jvde Tower?

38:54.576 --> 38:57.968
(Dehua Ward)

39:00.880 --> 39:02.360
Underground canal in the southwest

39:02.760 --> 39:03.760
(Prince Li's mansion)
starts from Prince Li's mansion

39:03.760 --> 39:05.679
(Jvde Tower, Wuwei Zhai)
via Jvde Tower, Wuwei Zhai,

39:05.679 --> 39:06.960
straight to the transport dock.

39:06.960 --> 39:07.679
(Transport Dock)

39:07.679 --> 39:09.776
The middle passage
is the main flood drainage canal,

39:10.280 --> 39:12.670
(Dehua Ward, Ziyun Ward)
via Dehua Ward, Ziyun Ward,

39:12.670 --> 39:14.159
connecting to the Yongding River.

39:17.159 --> 39:17.880
Ye Li.

39:19.760 --> 39:21.360
That way leads to the transport dock.

39:23.240 --> 39:25.840
The West Market water inlet
diverges from the river.

39:26.039 --> 39:27.880
It's highly populated and hard to hide.

39:28.079 --> 39:30.679
The passage to the imperial city
is heavily guarded.

39:31.039 --> 39:33.639
If he wanted
to leave the capital unnoticed,

39:34.039 --> 39:35.159
he'd only take this passage,

39:35.519 --> 39:37.776
the main flood drainage canal
leading to the outskirts.

39:39.360 --> 39:40.559
I know who you're looking for.

39:42.039 --> 39:43.240
You're looking for Mo Jingli.

39:44.679 --> 39:45.960
No need to hide it from me.

39:46.119 --> 39:47.360
I've figured it out.

39:47.760 --> 39:49.519
A fire broke out
at the Prince Li's Mansion,

39:49.519 --> 39:51.519
burning Prince Li
and several of his close aides.

39:51.960 --> 39:53.840
But now it seems he didn't die.

39:54.360 --> 39:56.920
Not bad. You could figure that out.

39:57.760 --> 39:58.760
It's nothing.

39:59.360 --> 40:01.079
For a top assassin,

40:01.159 --> 40:03.519
combing through subtle clues,

40:03.840 --> 40:05.360
and exposing the truth,

40:05.840 --> 40:07.840
is a basic requisite.

40:10.559 --> 40:11.559
Rest assured.

40:11.880 --> 40:13.360
I have my own rules.

40:14.079 --> 40:16.519
As an assassin, I stick
to the unbreakable rule,

40:16.639 --> 40:19.559
which is to keep secrets
for the employers.

40:21.360 --> 40:23.880
I'd swallow this secret,

40:24.079 --> 40:25.360
never spread a word about it.

40:27.119 --> 40:29.159
Do you belong
to some assassin organization?

40:29.679 --> 40:31.639
Or are you a lone swordsman?

40:33.960 --> 40:35.320
I can't tell you that.

40:35.960 --> 40:37.240
Your last attempt on my life

40:37.559 --> 40:39.960
was your first assassination mission,
wasn't it?

40:41.639 --> 40:42.519
How did you know?

40:46.639 --> 40:49.079
Seems we share quite the connection.

40:49.840 --> 40:51.599
Well, when this is over,

40:51.639 --> 40:53.639
if you need help, find me.

40:54.280 --> 40:55.760
Considering our connection,

40:56.360 --> 40:57.639
I can give you a discount.

41:12.720 --> 41:19.600
(Iron)

41:48.999 --> 41:49.639
Be careful.

41:56.320 --> 41:56.960
Lots of people.

42:00.920 --> 42:01.559
Go!

42:38.928 --> 42:41.712
(Preview)

42:42.760 --> 42:43.320
Your Highness.

42:44.119 --> 42:47.119
The person ahead seems
to be Princess Ding.

42:47.199 --> 42:50.079
Princess Ding interfered with
Imperial Court of Judicial Review affairs.

42:50.079 --> 42:53.280
We await the discerning judgement
of you both, Your Majesties.

42:53.440 --> 42:54.704
We fought with our lives

42:55.920 --> 42:57.960
to secure the situation we have today.

42:58.280 --> 42:59.760
You saw Master Zhu again?

42:59.880 --> 43:01.360
He must be living in the capital.

43:02.999 --> 43:05.456
But I've searched
every corner of the city,

43:06.280 --> 43:07.960
and found no trace of him.

43:15.736 --> 43:22.328
♪Memories hold you back
from fulfilling your dreams♪

43:25.912 --> 43:32.056
♪Only by moving forward
can you find reunion♪

43:34.264 --> 43:37.496
♪Endings only mark new routes♪

43:37.720 --> 43:43.736
♪It's all part of the scenery♪

43:44.056 --> 43:47.480
♪To the horizon's call♪

43:47.544 --> 43:54.104
♪Your journey hasn't started♪

43:55.160 --> 43:59.096
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

43:59.096 --> 44:04.792
♪Both joy and grief
make the trip worthwhile♪

44:05.304 --> 44:13.912
♪Trying to catch up
to your own lost shadow♪

44:14.808 --> 44:20.312
♪Within the wilds, echoes thrive♪

44:20.312 --> 44:25.816
♪Clear mind leads to a clear path♪

44:25.880 --> 44:29.944
♪Be grateful to your losses♪

44:30.232 --> 44:35.456
♪Make your steps weightless♪

44:36.056 --> 44:39.768
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

44:39.800 --> 44:45.464
♪Let time embrace you
and wash away the past♪

44:46.232 --> 44:54.200
♪Put every twist behind you,
drift leisurely through time♪

44:55.608 --> 45:00.856
♪Make headway against the wind,
let mountains bow to your pace♪

45:01.112 --> 45:07.016
♪Rush towards a life without regret♪

45:07.016 --> 45:11.136
♪Let your nature burst free♪

45:11.352 --> 45:16.088
♪Unbound by form♪

45:17.304 --> 45:21.576
♪Let your nature burst free♪

45:21.816 --> 45:27.256
♪Unbound by form♪
